    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:My scouts report they are defending the entrance of the post with teachers and evangelists.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:It should be easy to pick them off at range.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:Wait, what is that I see?
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:They are marching against us now! They must have seen us preparing an assault.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:Wait until you see the whites of their eyes before placing units on the battlefield.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:If you see a teacher coming counter with a Shepherd.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:And counter the evangelists with teachers.
