PostDialogue:
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:Congratulations on defeating the Diabolonians and retaking the guard post.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:But, know that our work to resist the craftiness of the Diabolonians continues.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:We must continue protecting the city of Mansoul from threats without as well as within.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:But you did good work today.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:As a reward, go to the market and unlock the shield ability.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:You can use this ability on a unit to prevent it from being damaged for a short time.
    Statement:
        Speaker:Captain Resistance
        LeftImage:0
        RightImage:None
        Dialogue:Rest until next time you are needed.